title: prompt()
brief: Prompt for input from the user.
----

<p>The bottom row of the <tt>lumail</tt> mail-client is designated as the message area, but it is also used to prompt for input.</p>
<p>The <tt>prompt()</tt> function allows you to query a user for input.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
input = prompt( "my prompt" );
<a href="msg.html">msg</a>( "You entered: " .. input );
</pre>

<p class="seealso">See also <a href="prompt_yn.html">prompt_yn</a>.</p>